{"tid":2173500,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先俾個呃錢電話大媽鬧我仆街","createTime":"2020-08-25T09:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T10:55:40.000Z","uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c61499f88a744b8fb2a3a3a5a929766288aaa876","tid":2173500,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"已經用緊聰明台個來電管家<br />\n但係都成日接到啲咩入境事務處呃錢電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次我都一定會同佢慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜次次都俾佢哋識穿我係香港人好快級我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日個大媽問完我個名<br />\n跟住問我身分證幾多號<br />\n我以為得米諗住睇吓佢點呃我錢<br />\n佢講左句「你媽的事」<br />\n果下我聽唔到問句什麼事<br />\n然後佢好L惡咁大聲講「你仆街啦」<br />\n跟住級L左我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呃錢都呃到咁L惡"},{"pid":"8494e429f68234c47339fe540aea4c8ba61c250f","tid":2173500,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"次次我都扮鬼嚇鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n「我夜晚一定跟住你」"},{"pid":"db3ceb009e234f9842dbbdcb70994a79414cbb69","tid":2173500,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8494e429f68234c47339fe540aea4c8ba61c250f","tid":2173500,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"次次我都扮鬼嚇鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n「我夜晚一定跟住你」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e232f2b17595b499df0b3c6d41fb54e05ac81d76","tid":2173500,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}